OL,3,CLondon Fire Brigade makes 'significant
OL,4,Cimprovements' since 2022
OL,6,FLondon Fire Brigade (LFB) has made
OL,7,F"significant improvements" in
OL,8,Fperformance since 2022, the fire
OL,9,Finspectorate has said.
OL,11,FHis Majesty's Inspectorate of
OL,12,FConstabulary and Fire & Rescue
OL,13,FServices (HMICFRS) said in a review
OL,14,Fpublished on Friday that LFB is
OL,15,F"outstanding" at responding to major
OL,16,Fincidents, praising the brigade's
OL,17,F"significant" role in counterterrorism.
