OL,3,CLondon Fire Brigade makes 'significant
OL,4,Cimprovements' since 2022
OL,6,FIn 2022, HMICFRS found that the fire
OL,7,Fservice required improvement in
OL,8,Feffectively and efficiently keeping
OL,9,Fpeople safe and secure from fires, as
OL,10,Fwell as looking after its staff.
OL,12,FIn the same year, it placed LFB under
OL,13,Fspecial measures after an independent
OL,14,Freview found that the fire service was
OL,15,F"institutionally misogynist and
OL,16,Fracist".
OL,18,FIt was taken out of the enhanced level
OL,19,Fof monitoring earlier this year.
