OL,3,CLondon Fire Brigade makes 'significant
OL,4,Cimprovements' since 2022
OL,6,FLondon fire commissioner Andy Roe said
OL,7,Fthe latest report "provides a clear
OL,8,Fassessment of the positive change" the
OL,9,Fbrigade has made.
OL,11,FHMICFRS said the brigade has
OL,12,Fsignificantly improved its ability to
OL,13,Frespond effectively to a terrorist
OL,14,Fattack through investment in equipment
OL,15,Fand training and that it has a "good
OL,16,Fsystem" for home fire safety visits.
OL,18,FIt also said that LFB is making "good
OL,19,Fprogress" in its efforts to improve
OL,20,Fculture.
