OL,3,CLondon Fire Brigade makes 'significant
OL,4,Cimprovements' since 2022
OL,6,FHowever, the brigade was urged to do
OL,7,Fmore to recruit a more diverse
OL,8,Fworkforce and to improve and build
OL,9,Fstaff trust and confidence when
OL,10,Fdealing with poor behaviour.
OL,12,FHis Majesty's Inspector of Fire and
OL,13,FRescue Services Lee Freeman said he
OL,14,Fwas "pleased" to find the
OL,15,Fimprovements, saying the brigade has a
OL,16,Fbetter understanding of risk and
OL,17,Femergencies.
