OL,3,CLondon Fire Brigade makes 'significant
OL,4,Cimprovements' since 2022
OL,6,FHe went on: "It also continues to
OL,7,Frespond quickly to fires, and we have
OL,8,Fgraded it as outstanding in responding
OL,9,Fto major and multi-agency incidents.
OL,11,F"However, it still needs to improve
OL,12,Fhow it identifies and develops high-
OL,13,Fpotential staff and how it manages
OL,14,Findividual performance and development
OL,15,Freviews.
OL,17,F"While there is still more to do, it
OL,18,Fis evident that the brigade
OL,19,Funderstands where to make these
OL,20,Ffurther improvements and has
OL,21,Fachievable plans for them."
