OL,3,CLondon Fire Brigade makes 'significant
OL,4,Cimprovements' since 2022
OL,6,FMr Roe said the brigade is working to
OL,7,F"transform" the culture of the
OL,8,Forganisation.
OL,10,FHe added: "We are committed to
OL,11,Fmaintaining our progress over future
OL,12,Fyears, delivering further change, and
OL,13,Fensuring that we provide the service
OL,14,Fthat our staff and our communities
OL,15,Fdeserve.
OL,17,F"This is not the end of our journey,
OL,18,Fand every day we will strive to do
OL,19,Fbetter to ensure we remain trusted to
OL,20,Fserve and protect London."
